    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated An-Nazzal:\n\nAli came to the gate of the courtyard (of the Mosque) and drank (water) while he was standing and said, Some people dislike to drink while standing, but I saw the Prophet (ﷺ) doing (drinking water) as you have seen me doing now.',
