    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Sahl bin Sa`d:\n\nAllahs Messenger (ﷺ) was offered something to drink. He drank of it while on his right was a boy and on his left were some elderly people. He said to the boy, May I give these (elderly) people first? The boy said, By Allah, O Allahs Messenger (ﷺ)! I will not give up my share from you to somebody else. On that Allahs Messenger (ﷺ) placed the cup in the hand of that boy.',
