    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Urwa:\n\nAisha used to recommend at-Talbina for the sick and for such a person as grieved over a dead person. She used to say, I heard Allahs Messenger (ﷺ) saying, at-Talbina gives rest to the heart of the patient and makes it active and relieves some of his sorrow and grief.',
