      ' Narrated `Abdullah bin `Umar:\n\nAllahs Messenger (ﷺ) said, There is neither Adha (no contagious disease is conveyed to others without Allahs permission) nor Tiyara, but an evil omen may be in three a woman, a house or an animal.',
