    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Asma:\n\nA woman asked the Prophet (ﷺ) saying, 0 Allahs Messenger (ﷺ)! My daughter got measles and her hair fell out. Now that I got her married, may I let her use false hair? He said (to her), Allah has cursed the lady who lengthens hair artificially and the one who gets her hair lengthened artificially.',
