      ' Narrated Anas:\n\nAllahs Messenger (ﷺ) was neither a Fahish (one who had a bad tongue) nor a Sabbaba (one who abuses others) and he used to say while admonishing somebody, What is wrong with him? May dust be on his forehead!',
