    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Jundub:\n\nWhile the Prophet (ﷺ) was walking, a stone hit his foot and stumbled and his toe was injured. He then (quoting a poetic verse) said, You are not more than a toe which has been bathed in blood in Allahs Cause.',
