    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Abu Huraira:\n\nThe Prophet (ﷺ) said, The most awful (meanest) name in Allahs sight. Sufyan said more than once, The most awful (meanest) name in Allahs sight is (that of) a man calling himself king of kings. Sufyan said, Somebody else (i.e. other than Abu Az-Zinad, a sub-narrator) says: What is meant by The king of kings is Shahan Shah.,',
