    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Abu Bakra:\n\nAllahs Messenger (ﷺ) said, Shall I inform you of the biggest of the great sins? They said, Yes, O Allahs Apostle! He said, To join partners in worship with Allah, and to be undutiful to ones parents. \n\n Narrated Bishr:\n\nas above, adding: The Prophet (ﷺ) was reclining (leaning) and then he sat up saying, And I warn you against giving a false statement. And he kept on saying that warning so much so that we said, Would that he had stopped.',
