      ' Narrated Said bin Jubair:\nIbn Abbas was asked, How old were you when the Prophet (ﷺ) died? He replied. At that time I had been circumcised. At that time, people did not circumcise the boys till they attained the age of puberty. Said bin Jubair said, Ibn Abbas said, When the Prophet died, I had already been circumcised.  \n\n Said ibn Jubair said, Ibn Abbas said, When the Prophet (ﷺ) died, I had already been circumcised. ',
