      ' Narrated Ibn `Abbas:\n\nThe Prophet (ﷺ) used to invoke Allah at the time of distress, saying, La ilaha illal-lahu Al-`Azim, al- Halim, La ilaha illal-lahu Rabbu-s-samawati wal-ard wa Rabbu-l-arsh il-azim.',
