    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated `Aisha:\n\nThe boys used to be brought to the Prophet (ﷺ) and he used to invoke for Allahs blessing upon them. Once an infant was brought to him and it urinated on his clothes. He asked for water and poured it over the place of the urine and did not wash his clothes.',
