    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated `Aisha:\n\nThe Prophet (ﷺ) said, O Allah! Make us love Medina as You made us love Mecca, or more, and transfer the fever that is in it, to Al-Juhfa. O Allah! Bless our Mudd and our Sam (kinds of measures).',
