    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Ibn `Abbas:\n\nAllahs Messenger (ﷺ) said, Seventy thousand people of my followers will enter Paradise without accounts, and they are those who do not practice Ar-Ruqya and do not see an evil omen in things, and put their trust in their Lord.',
