    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Ibn `Umar:\n\nThe Prophet; said, The people of Paradise will enter Paradise, and the people of the (Hell) Fire will enter the (Hell) Fire: then a call-maker will get up (and make an announcement) among them, O the people of the (Hell) Fire! No death anymore ! And O people of Paradise! No death (anymore) but Eternity.',
