    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Haritha bin Wahb:\n\nI heard the Prophet (ﷺ) mentioning the Lake-Fount (Al-Kauthar), saying, (The width of the Lake-Fount) is equal to the distance between Medina and Sana (capital of Yemen).\n\nHaritha said that he heard the Prophet saying that his Lake-Fount would be as large as the distance between Sana and Medina. Al- Mustaurid said to Haritha, Didnt you hear him talking about the vessels? He said, No. Al- Mustaurid said, The vessels are seen in it as (numberless as) the stars.',
