    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Anas bin Malik:\n\nThe Prophet (ﷺ) said, Allah puts an angel in charge of the uterus and the angel says, O Lord, (it is) semen! O Lord, (it is now ) a clot! O Lord, (it is now) a piece of flesh. And then, if Allah wishes to complete its creation, the angel asks, O Lord, (will it be) a male or a female? A wretched (an evil doer) or a blessed (doer of good)? How much will his provisions be? What will his age be? So all that is written while the creature is still in the mothers womb.',
